# Expressions

snippet printf
abbr printf("${1}"${2:#:here});${0}
    printf("${1}"${2:#:here});${0}

snippet printf_ln
alias pr
abbr printf("${1}\n"${2:#:here});${0}
    printf("${1}\n"${2:#:here});${0}

